The artifact is a normal JVM jar with `.class` files, so I won’t mark it `not-for-native-image`. There is no separate Maven tests artifact, but the published `core-3.1.0-sources.jar` includes Trove’s `*Test.java` files, so I’ll use that Maven source jar for both source and test code URLs.
